{{> header}}

<h2>Verify your email address</h2>
<p>Hi {{firstName}},</p>
<p>
  Thanks for signing up! Use the one-time code below to verify your email address.
  It expires in <strong>{{expiryMinutes}} minutes</strong>.
</p>

<div class="otp-box">
  <div class="otp">{{otp}}</div>
  <small>Enter this code in the app to complete verification</small>
</div>

<p style="font-size:13px;color:#64748b;">
  If you did not create an account, no action is required — simply ignore this email.
</p>

{{> footer}}
